000Z","msg":"仆街，陳雲出山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩達就話2020出黎再選"},{"pid":"9a0eab946209c11311e774abf1c606f3f5c94441","tid":1264640,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T21:33:14.000Z","msg":"屌你真係要再推自已個post<br />\n兩個星期前講既，小心帶風向或者突然扮同路人既仆街！"},{"pid":"a503a597a1025799b997339bf14204470fb3a2e8","tid":1264640,"uid":58616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T21:39:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"363c045fc65795db103ba2f63ba94fdd576be7e7","tid":1264640,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T21:58:34.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"cd97b6fa0f05b317dd06f9455fa6c85f34b802b4","tid":1264640,"uid":269991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a369566bc10a1c82e3116064916132b63b04e628","tid":1264640,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:53:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544391/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544391/page/1</a><br />\n放低做個紀錄<br />\n連達哥都轉軑出黎做同路人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}